        "content": "<p>Is there a way to export a structure field right away when defining the structure? <br>\nSomething like</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">class</span> <span class=\"n\">Box</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">α</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"n\">where</span>\n  <span class=\"kn\">export</span> <span class=\"n\">box</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>as a shorthand for </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">class</span> <span class=\"n\">Box</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">α</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"n\">where</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">box</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">export</span> <span class=\"n\">Box</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">box</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
